reviews.text: Such a delightful small town. Many places on the beach where you can find calm and peace. You can have a long walk along a sea or just grab a bike and ride. Lovely old beach huts. Didn’t have a lot of time but would love to come back to explore more!
Absolutely apalling excuse for a train station. Needs cleaning up and modernising. Rail replacement services tend to be in use more than the train services.
Perfect little branch line terminus. Reliable, simple services to Ipswich. Clean and reasonably neat. Could do with a lick of paint, but no real complaints.
